      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32">

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center animate-slide-up">
          <h1
            class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-slate-200 to-slate-400">
            L'alternative open-source <br> à Linktree.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
            Plinkk est conçu pour être rapide, beau et respectueux de votre vie privée. <br class="hidden sm:block">
            Une expérience fluide, personnalisable et facile à auto-héberger.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
            <a href="https://github.com/PlinkkCorp/plinkk" target="_blank"
              class="rounded-xl bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-200 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white transition-all hover:scale-105">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 inline-block mr-2 -mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path
                  d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z" />
              </svg>
              Star sur GitHub
            </a>
            <a href="/docs" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-violet-300 transition-colors">
              Documentation <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Grid -->
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
          <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">

            <div
              class="flex flex-col bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-violet-500/30 transition-colors group">
              <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
                <div
                  class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 group-hover:bg-indigo-500/20 transition-colors">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Open Source
              </dt>
                <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-slate-400">
                <p class="flex-auto">
                  Le code de <strong>Plinkk Backend</strong> est open source sous <strong>Plinkk Communautary Licence (PCL)</strong>.<br>
                  <a href="https://github.com/PlinkkCorp/plinkk-backend/blob/master/LICENCE" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-violet-300">Voir la licence complète</a>.<br>
                  <br>
                  <button type="button"
                  class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-violet-300 hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-violet-400"
                  onclick="const d=document.getElementById('pcl-usage-details');d.hidden=!d.hidden;">
                  Découvrir les usages autorisés
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform" id="pcl-usage-arrow" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                  </svg>
                  </button>
                  <div id="pcl-usage-details" hidden class="mt-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-800/80 p-4 text-sm text-slate-300 border border-violet-900/30">
                  <strong>Usages autorisés :</strong> consultation, apprentissage, contribution, usage strictement privé ou universitaire.<br>
                  La technologie Plinkk (hors backend) est 100% réutilisable et open source pour vos propres projets personnels, académiques et commerciaux.<br>
                  <strong>Interdit :</strong> tout usage commercial, associatif, auto-hébergement ou déploiement public du backend sans accord écrit.<br>
                  Les crédits Plinkk doivent être conservés.<br>
                  <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Pour toute demande d'autorisation spécifique, contactez l'équipe Plinkk.</span>
                  </div>
                </p>
                <script>
                  // Optionally rotate the arrow on open/close
                  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
                  const btn = document.querySelector('button[onclick*="pcl-usage-details"]');
                  const details = document.getElementById('pcl-usage-details');
                  const arrow = document.getElementById('pcl-usage-arrow');
                  if (btn && arrow && details) {
                    btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
                    arrow.style.transform = details.hidden ? '' : 'rotate(180deg)';
                    });
                  }
                  });
                </script>
                </dd>
              </div>

            <div
              class="flex flex-col bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-fuchsia-500/30 transition-colors group">
              <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
                <div
                  class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-fuchsia-500/10 group-hover:bg-fuchsia-500/20 transition-colors">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-fuchsia-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Personnalisation
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-slate-400">
                <p class="flex-auto">Exprimez-vous avec des thèmes dynamiques, des arrière-plans animés, des effets de
                  verre et bien plus encore.</p>
              </dd>
            </div>

            <div
              class="flex flex-col bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group">
              <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
                <div
                  class="h-10 w-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                      d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Performance
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-slate-400">
                <p class="flex-auto">Construit avec Node.js et Prisma pour une rapidité maximale. Vos pages se chargent
                  instantanément.</p>
              </dd>
            </div>

          </dl>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Section -->
        <div class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-40 lg:px-8">
          <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">L'équipe</h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
              Les passionnés derrière le projet Plinkk.
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul role="list"
            class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">

            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/Klaynight-dev" target="_blank" class="group block">
                <div class="relative aspect-[3/2] w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                  <img
                    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                    src="https://github.com/Klaynight-dev.png?size=400" alt="">
                  <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent opacity-80">
                  </div>
                  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6">
                    <h3
                      class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-violet-300 transition-colors">
                      Klaynight-dev</h3>
                    <p class="text-base leading-7 text-slate-300">Lead Developer & UI/UX</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </a>
            </li>

            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/Marvideo2009" target="_blank" class="group block">
                <div class="relative aspect-[3/2] w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                  <img
                    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                    src="https://github.com/Marvideo2009.png?size=400" alt="">
                  <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900 via-slate-900/20 to-transparent opacity-80">
                  </div>
                  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6">
                    <h3
                      class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-violet-300 transition-colors">
                      Marvideo2009</h3>
                    <p class="text-base leading-7 text-slate-300">Backend & DevOps</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </a>
            </li>

          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
